# Native folders are regenerated by EAS Build/expo prebuild from app.json +
# plugins/ on every build (managed/CNG workflow) — committing them causes
# EAS to use the stale committed version instead of regenerating, silently
# skipping any config plugin changes (this caused a real, hard-to-diagnose
# build failure — see plugins/withNotificationManifestFix.js).
